column2: Must be a valid IP CIDR range of the form x.x.x.x/x
Must be a valid EC2 instance type
The IP address range that can be used to SSH to the EC2 instances
[u't1.micro', u't2.micro', u't2.small', u't2.medium', u'm1.small', u'm1.medium', u'm1.large']

{u'Fn::Base64': {u'Fn::Join': [u'', [u'#!/bin/bash -xe
', u'apt -y update
', u'DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive apt-get -y upgrade
', u'apt install -y docker.io screen
', u'mkdir /ethereum
', {u'Fn::If': [u'IsNVME', {u'Fn::Join': [u'', [u'mkfs.ext4 -F /dev/nvme0n1
', u'mount /dev/nvme0n1 /ethereum
', u'chmod a+w /ethereum/
', u'echo UUID=`sudo blkid -s UUID -o value /dev/disk/by-id/nvme-Amazon*` /ethereum/ ext4 discard,defaults,nofail 0 2 | sudo tee -a /etc/fstab
']]}, u'']}, u'export INSTANCEID=$(curl -s http://169.254.169.254/latest/meta-data/instance-id)
', u'docker pull myetherwallet/docker-geth-lb:geth-instance
', u"/usr/bin/screen -m -d -S docker docker run -e WS_SECRET='", {u'Ref': u'ETHStatsPassword'}, u"' -e WS_SERVER='", {u'Fn::GetAtt': [u'EthstatsInstance', u'PublicIp']}, u'' -e INSTANCE_NAME="mew-geth-instance-$INSTANCEID" -it -p 8545:8545 -p 30303:30303 -v /ethereum:/root/.ethereum --restart unless-stopped myetherwallet/docker-geth-lb:geth-instance 
']]}}
Password to connect to ethstats server

{u'Fn::Base64': {u'Fn::Join': [u'', [u'#!/bin/bash -xe
', u'apt update -y
', u'apt install -y docker.io screen
', u'docker pull myetherwallet/docker-geth-lb:ethstats-instance
', u"/usr/bin/screen -m -d -S docker docker run -it -e WS_SECRET='", {u'Ref': u'ETHStatsPassword'}, u"' -p 3000:3000 myetherwallet/docker-geth-lb:ethstats-instance
"]]}}
Name of an existing EC2 KeyPair to enable SSH access to the instance
IP address of the ethstats server
[{u'ToPort': u'8545', u'IpProtocol': u'tcp', u'CidrIp': u'0.0.0.0/0', u'FromPort': u'8545'}, {u'ToPort': u'22', u'IpProtocol': u'tcp', u'CidrIp': {u'Ref': u'SSHLocation'}, u'FromPort': u'22'}]
